used the salvage equipment</i>

35:10.691 --> 35:12.401
<i>to raise the truck, get the gold.</i>

35:12.401 --> 35:15.738
<i>Sank the truck again and put
the equipment back on Ray-Ray's truck.</i>

35:15.738 --> 35:18.157
<i>What I didn't notice was
that it was still wet.</i>

35:23.955 --> 35:26.791
