that gives you a better life?"

35:28.501 --> 35:29.335
What?

35:30.211 --> 35:33.005
<i>Wagon Train.</i> You wouldn't remember it.

35:33.881 --> 35:36.509
Barbara Stanwyck?

35:36.509 --> 35:37.802
Yeah, I loved her.

35:38.386 --> 35:40.304
Delly's got a little bit of that in her.

35:40.304 --> 35:41.639
You know, I...

35:42.181 --> 35:45.017
