and I won't be here when you do.

37:37.463 --> 37:38.839
Where are you gonna be?

37:39.966 --> 37:41.092
Iris is gone.

37:41.759 --> 37:42.802
Delly is gone.

37:43.469 --> 37:46.264
<i>And you are right back here
where you started.</i>

37:47.390 --> 37:48.391
<i>Nowhere.</i>

37:49.058 --> 37:51.811
<i>I was really pulling for you and Iris.</i>

37:52.603 --> 37:54.146
<i>That Delly...</i>

37:55.856 --> 37:57.900
